&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;USP &amp;lt;795&amp;gt;, USP &amp;lt;797&amp;gt;, and USP &amp;lt;800&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;State Board of Pharmacy and DEA regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;FDA guidance documents and DSCSA requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;NABP requirements, OSHA regulations, and Hazardous Drug handling requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Maintain inspection readiness at all times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
