&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;14:1-14:359;742-1100&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We&#39;re specifically looking for an already-experienced compounding pharmacy technician&lt;/strong&gt; — this is not an entry-level role. An active &lt;strong&gt;Florida State Pharmacy Technician License is required, no exceptions&lt;/strong&gt;. If you&#39;re proactive, open-minded, hungry to grow, and comfortable owning a project from start to finish with minimal oversight, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
