&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;10:1-10:18;206-223&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;12:1-12:411;225-635&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a reliable, fast-moving &lt;strong&gt;Runner&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Shipping team. This role is key to keeping our shipping operation running smoothly — you&#39;ll be the person making sure workstations stay stocked, materials keep flowing, and daily shipping deadlines get met. You&#39;ll work closely with Shippers and Shipping Supervisors in a fast-paced warehouse environment where no two hours look exactly the same.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;14:1-14:168;637-804&quot;&gt;If you thrive on movement, take initiative without waiting to be told, and enjoy being part of a team that has to hit deadlines every single day, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;16:1-16:18;806-823&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;18:1-23:76;825-1348&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;18:1-18:94;825-918&quot;&gt;Restock shipping stations with boxes, coolers, gel packs, labels, and other supplies (~50%)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;19:1-19:80;919-998&quot;&gt;Keep work areas organized, clean, and compliant with safety procedures (~40%)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;20:1-20:100;999-1098&quot;&gt;Communicate with Shipping Supervisors and teammates about priorities and operational needs (~10%)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;21:1-21:94;1099-1192&quot;&gt;Support Shippers by ensuring materials are always available to maintain continuous workflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;22:1-22:80;1193-1272&quot;&gt;Follow all company safety procedures and standard operating procedures (SOPs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;23:1-23:76;1273-1348&quot;&gt;Help the team hit daily productivity, quality, and on-time shipping goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
