&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;145&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;149&quot; data-end=&quot;161&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;164&quot; data-end=&quot;551&quot;&gt;At &lt;strong data-start=&quot;167&quot; data-end=&quot;187&quot;&gt;The Pharmacy Hub&lt;/strong&gt;, we collaborate with &lt;strong data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;314&quot;&gt;pharmaceutical brands, manufacturers, health brands, telemedicine providers, and healthcare companies&lt;/strong&gt; to deliver essential products &lt;strong data-start=&quot;345&quot; data-end=&quot;370&quot;&gt;directly to patients.&lt;/strong&gt; Our expertise allows us to seamlessly distribute &lt;strong data-start=&quot;420&quot; data-end=&quot;487&quot;&gt;pharmaceuticals, medical devices, and other healthcare products&lt;/strong&gt; to consumers, ensuring greater accessibility and convenience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;133&quot; data-end=&quot;160&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;133&quot; data-end=&quot;158&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, operate, and monitor tablet press machines (e.g., rotary tablet press) according to SOPs and batch records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjust machine settings to optimize performance and ensure tablet quality (weight, hardness, thickness, etc.) •&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform routine maintenance and cleaning of equipment • Troubleshoot mechanical issues and escalate as needed •&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document production activity, inspections, and deviations accurately •&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adhere to all safety protocols, GMP guidelines, and standard operating procedures •&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support changeovers and assist with cleaning validation and documentation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with quality and production teams to resolve issues and meet production goals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1250&quot; data-end=&quot;1271&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1250&quot; data-end=&quot;1269&quot;&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;High school diploma or equivalent required, technical training a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;1+ year experience operating tablet press machinery preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Familiarity with cGMP regulations and cleanroom protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Good mechanical aptitude and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Ability to lift up to 50lbs and stand for extended periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Strong communication and teamwork skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Fluent in English and Spanish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1363&quot;&gt;Preferably &lt;strong&gt;State of Florida Pharmacy Technician License&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
